<div><div><div><div><div></div></div><p>美国疫苗公司Moderna。（AP）</p></div></div><div><p>美国疫苗公司莫德纳（Moderna）11月16日宣布，其生产的疫苗有94.5% 的有效率。这也超越了其竞争对手辉瑞（Pfizer）一周前宣布的其疫苗90%的有效性。</p></div><div><div><div></div></div><div><div></div></div></div><p>综合媒体11月16日报道，莫德纳当天发表声明称，根据一项III期大规模志愿者（3万）试验的中期数据，该公司研发的实验性疫苗mRNA-1273在预防新冠病毒（SARS-CoV-2）方面的有效性达到94.5%。这也使其成为美国第二种成功率极高的疫苗，超越了辉瑞。</p><div><div><blockquote><p lang="en" dir="ltr">We just announced that mRNA-1273, our COVID-19 vaccine candidate, has met its primary efficacy endpoint in the first interim analysis of the Phase 3 COVE study.<br>Read more: <a href="https://t.co/vYWEy8CKCv">https://t.co/vYWEy8CKCv</a> <a href="https://t.co/YuLubU1tlx">pic.twitter.com/YuLubU1tlx</a></p>&mdash; Moderna (@moderna_tx) <a href="https://twitter.com/moderna_tx/status/1328307041732071424?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 16, 2020</a></blockquote> </div></div><p>该消息一经发出，正准备“权力过渡”的拜登第一时间在推特表示祝贺。</p><p>拜登写道：“今天第二种疫苗的消息让我们更有理由感到希望。第一种疫苗与第二种疫苗的情况一样：我们还需要几个月的时间。在那之前，美国人需要继续保持社交距离和戴口罩来控制病毒（传播）。”</p><div><div><blockquote><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Today&#39;s news of a second vaccine is further reason to feel hopeful. What was true with the first vaccine remains true with the second: we are still months away. Until then, Americans need to continue to practice social-distancing and mask-wearing to get the virus under control.</p>&mdash; Joe Biden (@JoeBiden) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoeBiden/status/1328338687910928386?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 16, 2020</a></blockquote> </div></div><p>在莫德纳公司宣布疫苗有效性的两个小时后，一直忙于控诉“选举欺诈”的现任美国总统特朗普也在推特回应此事。这一次，他仍不忘将新冠疫情诬称为“中国瘟疫”。</p><p>特朗普在喊话“伟大的历史学家们”，称那些将终结疫情的“伟大发现”，都是在自己的任期内发生的。</p><div><div><blockquote><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Another Vaccine just announced. This time by Moderna, 95% effective. For those great “historians”, please remember that these great discoveries, which will end the China Plague, all took place on my watch!</p>&mdash; Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) <a href="https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1328341